snippet.title: TimeOut Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
In a city where the lives of humans are subjected to a time-based currency system, a hard-up detective goes on the hunt for a seller of fake time.

Release Date: May 8th
Platforms: PC & Mac
Release link: https://christopherlee.itch.io/timeout

Soundtrack: Kansas City Flashback - Golden Age Radio
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R0HE7rE38Ss
